{
  "stem": "9446.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So anyway, they told us you have to go somewhere else.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You can't be in that-- in that-- how do we call this-- border zone, you know, whatever.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then I remember being in Rovno, which is also in the eastern part of Poland-- a little town, Rovno.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was trying to get a job.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I couldn't get a job.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was a miserable life, terrible.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was almost starvation.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then eventually I was trying to get-- oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was trying to get to see some of my distant family in the-- [HORN HONKING]",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "On the way to Lvov-- please listen to this carefully-- on the way to Lvov, there is a little town called [NON-ENGLISH] I'm confused.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm sorry.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Forget about Lvov.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "On the way to [NON-ENGLISH], and I told you I have some distant family, [NON-ENGLISH], There is a little town called [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You could not get to [NON-ENGLISH] if you don't pass [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In that town of [NON-ENGLISH] we heard shooting still going on between the Russian-- between the Germans and the Poles.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The war was still going on there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And one day, I see no Pole, no shooting anymore.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I heard no shooting anymore.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I see German tanks there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And that was they occupied already [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Obviously they won the war in no time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It was what they call a Blitzkrieg, which means lightning speed, krieg-- war.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Krieg is war.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "In German, it's krieg.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I was with Germans there two days with the Nazis in [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "First thing they did, they-- ordered all the Jews to assemble in the marketplace in [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And they gave us an incredible job.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
